      "note_md": {
        "en": "Student status is for studies at universities, junior colleges, colleges of technology, specialized training colleges or Japanese language schools. Document packages are set by the Immigration Services Agency and the accepting school.",
        "zh-Hans": "留学资格适用于大学、短期大学、高等专门学校、专修学校或日语学校的学习。材料包由出入国在留管理厅和接收学校确定。"
      }
