    "stability_requirement_md": {
      "en": "Study in Japan states that COE or visa applications may require proof that the applicant can cover expenses while studying, such as savings, income certificates, or sponsor documentation.",
      "zh-Hans": "Study in Japan 说明申请认定证明书或签证时可能需要证明能够支付学习期间费用，例如存款、收入证明或担保人材料。"
    }
  },
  "timeline": {
    "application_processing_time_md": {
      "en": "The school usually acts as proxy for the Certificate of Eligibility. After the COE is issued, apply for a visa at a Japanese embassy or consulate. Period of stay is set case by case up to 4 years and 3 months.",
      "zh-Hans": "学校通常代理申请在留资格认定证明书。认定证明书签发后，向日本使领馆申请签证。居留期限按个案设定，最长 4 年 3 个月。"
    },
